            <p class="recipe-section__body">Using OpenCastle streamlines repetitive boilerplate — the convoy spawns parallel agents to generate server scaffolding, route handlers, validation, auth, and tests, while enforcing quality gates and review steps so you get a working API faster with consistent standards.</p>
