            <h3 class="recipe-section__heading">Step 1: Initialize</h3>
            <p class="recipe-section__body">Create a new directory, initialize git and npm, then run the OpenCastle initializer. During the interactive prompts, select your IDE and choose tech tools that match your server stack (e.g., <code>express</code> or <code>fastify</code>, <code>vitest</code>).</p>
            <div class="recipe-code">
              <div class="recipe-code__header">Terminal</div>
              <pre><code>$ mkdir task-api
$ cd task-api
$ git init
$ npm init -y
$ npx opencastle init</code></pre>
